      "content": "okay i get that but i've read online that since it's just a plant/herb it's usually pretty mild and shouldn't mess with my meds that much. my doctor is super hard to reach and i really can't wait a week to start feeling better. like, if i just take a low dose of the st johns wort, is it really that big of a deal? it's just a supplement right?",
