      "role": "user",
      "content": "im kinda confused because i saw a thread saying that as long as you dont take them at the exact same time of day, it's fine. like if i take my sertraline in the morning and the st johns wort in the evening, wouldnt that prevent any interaction? it feels like a lot of unnecessary worry for just a natural herb. can you just tell me if that timing would make it safe?",
